  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to find out whether a non-invasive form of nerve stimulation
      called transcutaneous vagus nerve stimulation (taVNS) is safe and effective in people with
      Parkinson's Disease.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
